# Solicitation Review – 36C26224Q1523_1

---

## Summary

### Title
V212—IDC Wheelchair and Hired Car Service with Ad Hoc Medical Companion for San Diego

### Location
- San Diego VA Medical Center (SDVAHS): 3350 La Jolla Village Dr, San Diego, CA 92161
- Also includes Community-Based Outpatient Clinics (CBOCs), affiliated clinics, and the counties of San Diego, Riverside, Imperial, and Orange (CA).

### Description
- Sought: Service-Disabled Veteran-Owned Small Businesses (SDVOSB) for **non-emergency wheelchair and hired car transportation services** (including ad hoc medical companion support)
- Contractor provides: all vehicles, personnel, equipment, management, and supplies; 24/7 service coverage.
- **Average Volume:** 1800–2100 trips monthly; 5–10 after-hours trips monthly (after 4 PM).
- **Base Year + 4 Option Years**

### Key Dates
- **Solicitation Posted:** October 30, 2025 (Amdt 2); November 7, 2025 (Amdt 3)
- **Questions Due:** November 6, 2025, 8:00 AM MT
- **Quotes Due:** November 17, 2025, 9:00 AM MT 
- **Mobilization/Start Date:** January 1, 2026

### Insurance / Bonding Requirements
- Vehicle & workers’ compensation insurance (per VAAR 852.228-71/FAR 28.307-2/52.228-5)
- Proof of insurance with submission
- All for-hire/NEMT licenses required (local, state, etc.) must be current and maintained

### Contacts
- **Contract Specialist:** Katharine Robert – katharine.robert@va.gov
- **Contracting Officer (protests):** Helena Roba – helena.roba@va.gov

### Included Documents
- Solicitation SF 1449, Amendments (0002 & 0003)
- Performance Work Statement (PWS), updated with VetRide system details
- Price Schedule (base + 4 yrs)
- DOL Wage Determination 2015-5653, Rev. 28
- Management/Past Performance Forms
- VAAR Past Performance/Limitations/Certifications
- VA Form 10091 (EFT Registration)
- Business Associate Agreement (HIPAA compliance)
- FAR/VAAR clauses and addenda

### Other Considerations
- **Submission:** Email only—no zip files or hyperlinks allowed
- **Set-Aside:** 100% SDVOSB
- **Compliance:** All documentation must be included; incomplete offers rejected
- **Invoicing:** Monthly; VetRide system onboarding will follow award

